---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
const issueNumber = 47;

const today = new Date();
const pad2 = (n: number) => String(n).padStart(2, "0");
const dateStamp = `${pad2(today.getDate())}.${pad2(today.getMonth() + 1)}.${today.getFullYear()}`;
---

<footer class="site-footer" role="contentinfo">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-col footer-brand">
      <div class="footer-brand-head">
        <span class="footer-brand-name">Dân Cư Mạng</span>
        <span class="footer-brand-issue">·{issueNumber}</span>
      </div>
      <p>Bản tin an ninh mạng cho người Việt. Miễn phí, không quảng cáo, mã nguồn mở.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-col">
      <div class="col-head">Nội dung</div>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/khoa-hoc/">Khóa học</a></li>
        <li><a href="/blog/">Blog &amp; Tin tức</a></li>
        <li><a href="/cong-cu/">Công cụ</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-col">
      <div class="col-head">Thực hành</div>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/cong-cu/kiem-tra-mat-khau/">Kiểm tra mật khẩu</a></li>
        <li><a href="/cong-cu/quiz-phishing/">Quiz lừa đảo</a></li>
        <li><a href="/cong-cu/checklist/">Checklist</a></li>
        <li><a href="/rss.xml">RSS feed</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-col footer-emergency">
      <div class="col-head">Khẩn cấp</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Tổng đài: <strong>113</strong></li>
        <li>Cục An toàn TT</li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://khonggianmang.vn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            khonggianmang.vn
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-bottom">
    <span>© {year} Dân Cư Mạng · MIT · CC BY-SA 4.0</span>
    <span class="footer-meta">
      SỐ {issueNumber} · {dateStamp} · STATIC · NO TRACKING
    </span>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-strong);
    background: var(--paper);
    margin-top: var(--space-section);
  }

  .footer-inner {
    max-width: var(--container);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 56px 28px 32px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.8fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  /* Brand block */
  .footer-brand-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .footer-brand-name {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--ink-strong);
  }
  .footer-brand-issue {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .footer-brand p {
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 320px;
  }

  /* Column heads (small caps editorial labels) */
  .col-head {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--ink-strong);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-strong);
  }

  .footer-col ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
  }

  .footer-col li,
  .footer-col a {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color var(--duration-fast);
  }
  .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

  .footer-emergency strong { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }

  /* Bottom rule */
  .footer-bottom {
    max-width: var(--container);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 16px 28px 36px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .footer-meta {
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
  }

  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .footer-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
      padding: 44px 20px 24px;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .footer-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
    .footer-bottom { justify-content: flex-start; padding: 16px 20px 32px; }
  }
</style>
